node.text: Warning: graphic content 😅 I wanted to thank @drghersi for my dream nose!! I have been back and forth wanting this since I was little, we tried filler 2 years ago but it didn’t give me the results I wanted. I am officially 4 weeks post surgery & I’ve never felt so confident 🥺 I am so so so happy & proud to announce to share with you all my amazing results. The amount of love I’ve received regarding my nose has been so unexpected especially on a platform like this so I also want to thank you guys for being so freaking awesome. Any questions you might have, feel free to slide in the DMs or directly contact @drghersi ❤️ amazing amazing amazing team of people backed up by his incredible talent #drghersi

node.text: Register for free for a chance to win a million dollars playing video games LINK IN BIO‼️ @the.ultimate.gamer is hosting the coolest tournament at the comfort of your own home. Anyone can participate, and for those asking what kind of games .... all of them! Download the Ultimate Gamer Arena and participate in weekly tournaments for cash prizes while you hone your skills leading up to the grand tournament in March 2021 💵🙏🏽  download and start playing today ! @the.ultimate.gamer program once downloaded will automatically record your stats while you climb the leaderboard and earn cash prizes. Don’t forget to register for free ‼️
